OL,3,CRoad rage driver who punched grandma:
OL,4,C'I thought she was a man'
OL,6,FA driver who punched a grandmother as
OL,7,Fshe sat in her car during a road rage
OL,8,Fincident told a court: "I thought it
OL,9,Fwas a guy".
OL,11,FJohnathan Barclay, 37, attacked the 62-
OL,12,Fyear-old woman through the open window
OL,13,Fof her car after pursuing her when she
OL,14,Fsounded her horn at him.
OL,16,FBarclay, of Main Street, Sewerby, near
OL,17,FBridlington, admitted assaulting the
OL,18,Fwoman, causing actual bodily harm and
OL,19,Fcareless driving in the incident on 16
OL,20,FDecember 2023. He was jailed for two
OL,21,Fyears.
