OL,3,CRoad rage driver who punched grandma:
OL,4,C'I thought she was a man'
OL,6,FHull Crown Court heard the victim was
OL,7,Fdriving on Promenade, Bridlington,
OL,8,Fwith her granddaughter in the
OL,9,Fpassenger seat, when Barclay got into
OL,10,Fhis car.
OL,12,FThe woman sounded her horn after he
OL,13,Fopened his door, obstructing the
OL,14,Ftraffic.
OL,16,FBarclay sped up behind her and cut in
OL,17,Ffront of her car, forcing her to stop.
OL,19,FHe shouted an insult at her before
OL,20,Fpunching her in the face through her
OL,21,Fopen window.
