OL,3,CRoad rage driver who punched grandma:
OL,4,C'I thought she was a man'
OL,6,FProsecutor Jennifer Gatland said: "The
OL,7,Fdefendant got back into his car and
OL,8,Fdrove off at speed, overtaking two
OL,9,Fother cars. It was a single punch and
OL,10,Fan act of road rage."
OL,12,FThe woman was taken to Scarborough
OL,13,FHospital with grazes and a split lip.
OL,15,FBarclay claimed he did not realise the
OL,16,Fvictim was a woman.
