OL,3,CRoad rage driver who punched grandma:
OL,4,C'I thought she was a man'
OL,6,FHe told the court: "It was a well-
OL,7,Fbuilt person with short hair. In my
OL,8,Fhead, I thought it was a guy that I
OL,9,Fwas having an altercation with and was
OL,10,Fgoing to punch. I was angry in
OL,11,Fgeneral. I was just angry. I was
OL,12,Fseeing red ` enraged.
OL,14,F"If I had known the person was female,
OL,15,FI think my actions would have been
OL,16,Ftotally different. There is no reason
OL,17,Fto punch anyone but there is no reason
OL,18,Fto punch a woman."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
