OL,3,CRoad rage driver who punched grandma:
OL,4,C'I thought she was a man'
OL,6,FHe added: "There may have been words
OL,7,Fexchanged. In my head, the person I
OL,8,Fwas walking up to was a man. I did not
OL,9,Fthink for one minute that this was an
OL,10,Fold lady that I was about to strike.
OL,12,FRachel Scott, mitigating, said: "What
OL,13,Fhe has done is dreadful. He has shown
OL,14,Fgenuine remorse. He apologises and is
OL,15,Fincredibly remorseful. He knows his
OL,16,Fbehaviour was absolutely disgusting."
