OL,3,CRoad rage driver who punched grandma:
OL,4,C'I thought she was a man'
OL,6,FJudge John Thackray KC said of the
OL,7,Fother driver: "She has a womanly
OL,8,Ffigure. There was no basis whatsoever
OL,9,Ffor him to assume that the person in
OL,10,Fthe car was a man. In a state of
OL,11,Fcomplete rage, he was prepared to hit
OL,12,Fa woman."
OL,14,FAs well as being jailed for two years
OL,15,FBarclay was given six penalty points.
